      <title>能源危机期间 Mercuria 的两位高管共享 10 亿美元收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/mercuria-s-top-duo-shared-1-billion-payday-amid-energy-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贸易公司 Mercuria Energy Group Ltd. 的两位高管在 2023 年分享了超过 10 亿美元的股息，这是历史上个人大宗商品交易商获得的最大股息之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/mercuria-s-top-duo-shared-1-billion-payday-amid-energy-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 17:29:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者担心消防基金影响，加州公用事业股下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/california-utilities-fall-as-investors-worry-about-fire-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州公用事业巨头爱迪生国际公司和太平洋天然气电力公司股价下跌，原因是投资者担心该州设立的野火基金的规模，该基金旨在为电力公司的设备与灾难性的野火有关时提供支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/california-utilities-fall-as-investors-worry-about-fire-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 17:19:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 KKR 正考虑以 70 亿英镑出售英国废物处理公司 Viridor</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/kkr-said-to-weigh-7-billion-sale-of-uk-recycling-firm-viridor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，KKR &amp; Co. 正在探索收购 Viridor Ltd. 的选项，包括可能的出售，包括债务在内，这家英国废物管理公司的估值可能高达 70 亿英镑（85 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/kkr-said-to-weigh-7-billion-sale-of-uk-recycling-firm-viridor</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 16:59:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员推迟美联储降息，美国国债收益率测试 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/treasuries-tumble-as-traders-push-back-next-fed-cut-to-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国就业报告表现强劲，增强了交易员和华尔街经济学家对美联储将推迟进一步降息的预期，导致规模 28 万亿美元的美国国债市场抛售加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/treasuries-tumble-as-traders-push-back-next-fed-cut-to-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 13:46:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冬季风暴席卷美国南部，近 3,000 个航班停飞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/winter-storm-grounds-more-than-2-000-us-flights-halts-trains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一场强大的冬季风暴席卷美国南部，导致近 3,000 个航班停飞，旅客列车停止运行，并威胁到该地区的大雪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/winter-storm-grounds-more-than-2-000-us-flights-halts-trains</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 13:05:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
